deck: A comic book adaption of the Canon movie Cyborg starring Jean-Claude Van Damme.
description:
Notes:

  • No cover date but indica has June 1989.
  • Art Director: Cynthia Grace
  • Special Advisor: M. D. Ward
  • Additional Design: K. "See"
  • "The Good, the Bad and the Lovely Backstage with the Cast of Cyborg" one page text piece featuring the starring cast acompanied by three black and white photos.
  • "Arming for Armageddon" one page text piece featuring the weapons of the future in the movie Cyborg accompanied by five black and white photos.
  • "Creating the Twenty-First Century Production Notes from the Set of 'Cyborg'" one page text piece featuring the creation of the movie settings of the future accompanied by three black and white photos.
  • "Van Damme Cyborg" one page color photo of the star Van Damme as Gibson Rickenbacker.
  • "From the Editor's Desk - Future Shocked A Conversation with "Cyborg" director Albert Pyun" 1/2 page text piece acompanied by one black and white photo.
  • "Vincent Klyn (Fender Tremolo) Cyborg" one page color photo of the star Vincent Tremolo as Fender Tremolo.
  • "Canon's Mouth Queries, Kudos, and Quibles From Cannon Video Viewers" one page text piece featuring two letters to Canon Video. Plus four black and white photos.
